FROM python:3.6

COPY requirements.txt .

RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt

COPY gunicorn.py .

COPY source /source

EXPOSE 5000

CMD ["gunicorn", "--chdir", "source", "--config", "./gunicorn.py", "flask_app:app"]
